            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Content Usage</h2>
            
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-blue-400 font-mono">Research and Articles</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-3 font-mono text-sm">
                The cybersecurity research, articles, and analysis provided on this website are:
              </p>
