            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-green-400 font-mono">> Links to External Sites</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 font-mono text-sm">
              This website may contain links to external websites that are not provided or maintained by us. 
              Please note that we do not guarantee the accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of any 
